  "detailed_description": "<strong>CONTROLLER HIGHLY RECOMMENDED</strong><br>Fast button-based low rule local multiplayer hockey game.<br>I think it's fun with friends, but most things are. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A = PASS.<br></li><li>B = SHOOT.<br></li><li>X = SAVE.<br></li><li>Y = CHECK.<br></li><li>STICK MOVE.<br></li><li>SHOULDER BUTTONS ALSO DO THINGS.</li></ul><br>If your friends leave you can practice against the kinda bad hockey robot.<br><br>Clap bombs, respect moms.",
